{"tid":2450893,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《我兒子Hunter》電影募資中！製片人：要拍拜登家族醜聞","createTime":"2021-03-17T17:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T00:59:58.000Z","uid":39464,"like":40,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3d6f04ab93bfa75dc076e7e2cfb3742fbc1da71f","tid":2450893,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T17:23:48.000Z","msg":"愛爾蘭電影製片夫婦麥卡愛西尼（Ann McElhinney）和麥卡阿立爾（Phelim McAleer）近日宣布為拍攝電影《我兒子杭特》（My Son Hunter），將籌措250萬美元資金，講述美國總統喬．拜登（Joe Biden）與兒子杭特（Hunter Biden）的醜聞。<br />\n<br />\n根據《華盛頓時報》（The Washington Times）報導，麥卡阿立爾指出，這部非好萊塢電影講述的是杭特和中國、俄羅斯、烏克蘭腐敗的業務往來，媒體和大型科技公司聯手掩蓋了《紐約郵報》對拜登家族的腐敗報導，「真相應該且需要盡可能地廣為人知，寓教於樂的電影是確保這件事的最好辦法。」<br />\n<br />\n麥卡愛西尼說，這部電影的故事非常令人著迷，他形容如同《王牌大賤諜》（Austin Powers）遇上《李爾王》（King Lear）再加上《紙牌屋》（House of Cards）的感覺，會讓觀眾察覺它難以言喻的娛樂性質；目前電影海報已經公布在推特募款帳號上，截至17日，只差8700美元就達到250萬美元的募資目標。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3470547\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3470547&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT60EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=9cceed98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3470547&h=86ec096d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3470547</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2021/mar/16/my-son-hunter-irish-filmmakers-behind-gosnell-laun/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtontimes.com%2Fnews%2F2021%2Fmar%2F16%2Fmy-son-hunter-irish-filmmakers-behind-gosnell-laun%2F&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT60EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=60d20c33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2021/mar/16/my-son-hunter-irish-filmmakers-behind-gosnell-laun/</a>"},{"pid":"1534c9e6544a34e4f86e65eabb6fe168ec26108f","tid":2450893,"uid":209422,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T18:01:15.000Z","msg":"希望佢哋唔好被消